This Morning host Phillip, 60, posted a sweet family picture as he and wife Stephanie celebrated their daughter's birthday with the family. Alongside the cosy family snap, Phillip penned in view of his three million followers: "Happy birthday gorgeous @mollyschofe," alongside a row of heart face emojis. The family enjoyed their meal at the high end Wolseley restaurant in the heart of London. Phillip's daughter Ruby also took to Instagram to wish her sister a good day. In a video she shared with her 83,000 followers, Ruby panned the dining table as she told her sister to have a "Happy birthday".